      "sc:description": "EnsembleFlex: Protein Structure Ensemble Analysis made easy \n- \nEnsembleFlex is a tool designed to perform dual-scale flexibility analysis of protein structure ensembles, encompassing both backbone and side-chain dynamics, in an easy, streamlined and reproducible way. It offers a user-friendly, no-coding graphical interface as well as a code-based option. It  complements experimental ensemble data analysis with predictive methods based on elastic network models.",
